data.description: Welcome to the perfect blend of spacious living and endless potential! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts an impressive 2,600 square feet of living space, ensuring there's room for everyone and everything. the kitchen offers ample cabinet space and an open layout. For those chilly nights or the occasional winter wonderland, you'll appreciate the newer central heat system and pellet stove ensuring you stay cozy no matter the weather outside. This home is in need of a little TLC..but that's where your imagination and creativity come into play! Transform this diamond in the rough into your mountain retreat. With some love and attention, you'll have a space that truly reflects your style and personality. With a fabulous location, situated on one of the best streets in Pollock Pines, you'll enjoy the serenity of this charming community while still having easy access to shopping and highway. If you're an outdoor enthusiast or a snow lover, you'll be thrilled to know that a quick drive will take you to the slopes of Sierra at Tahoe for endless winter fun.don't miss this fantastic opportunity. It's time to add your own flair to this spacious canvas and create memories that will last a lifetime.
